  "time_ut": 1662117525,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8  \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b85\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Financial aid will not be approved until pledges are received",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "International rating agency Fitch Ratings said that political instability could be detrimental to the implementation of reforms and access to IMF funding. Negotiations with official and private lenders on debt restructuring should be accelerated, although the time frame of any debt restructuring agreement remains uncertain, it said.",
        "The agency also indicated that the extended financing facility would not be approved by the IMF's Executive Committee until the government implemented pre-agreed measures, received financial commitments from official lenders, and made credible efforts to close the deal.",
        "In particular, the Fitch rating agency, which has pointed out that there is a need to make changes in tax policy and reduce unnecessary government spending, has said that political instability will have an impact on the implementation of reforms and even if credit restructuring is agreed, the IMF will also have an impact on the distribution of funds."
      ],
